channel.title: Comments on: Jose Gonzalez covers Massive Attack’s “Teardop” Mp3

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: I guess it isn't "old" since it is on the new album. Though mp3s of the cover have been around for years. Odd choice for inclusion on a new album. But then again, MUTE re-released Veneer several years after it had originally been released, so apparently Jose isn't in a hurry to release or record "new" material.
